text:
Same here...People have called me a wide range of things. To some I am too crazy, to some I sound dumb, to some I am annoying and too talkative, some say I laugh too loudly and some also think I am fake. 
So yeah, I have felt ashamed about how I behave a lot. To the point of hating myself. But I am learning to embrace that part of me now. Realising that I am genuinely like that. Hope to get to a point where it doesn't ashame me anymore. Wishing you the same as well :)
